quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,91,"And when it is said to them, "
  2,92,"And Moses had certainly brought you clear proofs. Then you took the calf [in worship] after that, while you were wrongdoers."
  2,93,"And [recall] when We took your covenant and raised over you the mount, [saying], "
  3,31,"Say, [O Muḥammad], "
  3,32,"Say, "
  3,33,"Indeed, Allāh chose Adam and Noah and the family of Abraham and the family of ʿImrān over the worlds -"